    "description": "<strong>嗨，学生们，欢迎来到学院！</strong><br>作为学校的院长，我很荣幸向你展示入学后等待你的一些功能。学院一直吸引着最好奇的人，这就是为什么你在这里。随意进来看看！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >学院</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1155460/extras/1c9c26ef7ec2ca46e1a7631187fc88a6.poster.avif?t=1593090475\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1155460/extras/1c9c26ef7ec2ca46e1a7631187fc88a6.webm?t=1593090475\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1155460/extras/1c9c26ef7ec2ca46e1a7631187fc88a6.mp4?t=1593090475\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>探索奇妙学院的每个角落。</strong><br>很棒，不是吗？不用担心，你将游览这些大厅并沉浸在其辉煌中。尽管学院以丰富多彩的景点而闻名，但也有较黑暗的角落。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >谜题</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1155460/extras/82e5d2b50e6926412e66a32672870690.poster.avif?t=1593090475\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1155460/extras/82e5d2b50e6926412e66a32672870690.webm?t=1593090475\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1155460/extras/82e5d2b50e6926412e66a32672870690.mp4?t=1593090475\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>解决200多个谜题。</strong><br>只有最优秀和最聪明的人才能进入学院，我们的谜题将证明你是否是其中之一。易于上手，但要专精却是非常有挑战性的，它们是对我们学生的终极考验。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1155460/extras/bb423e8e93f233fb86969bcad23e06e3.poster.avif?t=1593090475\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1155460/extras/bb423e8e93f233fb86969bcad23e06e3.webm?t=1593090475\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1155460/extras/bb423e8e93f233fb86969bcad23e06e3.mp4?t=1593090475\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>揭开笼罩着学校的神秘面纱，并探索它的秘密。</strong><br>这历史悠久的地方必然有很多故事。然而，这学期的故事将比以往所有故事都还耸动。你很快就会发现学院很多的秘密。但是，请记住，光将照明隐藏在黑暗的一切。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >角色</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1155460/extras/77f2c36c1246c76da485a3ac594c18a5.poster.avif?t=1593090475\" width=600 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1155460/extras/77f2c36c1246c76da485a3ac594c18a5.webm?t=1593090475\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1155460/extras/77f2c36c1246c76da485a3ac594c18a5.mp4?t=1593090475\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>遇见令人难忘的角色并与他们成为朋友</strong>（还有少数的敌人）。<br>学院无疑是一个特殊的地方。使它与众不同的是它的学生和员工。只有那些有能力做非凡事物的人才能在学院里度过时间，因此你将被最优秀的人环绕着。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >传说</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1155460/extras/b0d54aa2b79b1f9a9b245070e8e2b2d5.poster.avif?t=1593090475\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1155460/extras/b0d54aa2b79b1f9a9b245070e8e2b2d5.webm?t=1593090475\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1155460/extras/b0d54aa2b79b1f9a9b245070e8e2b2d5.mp4?t=1593090475\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>从谜题中喘口气，探索学院丰富的传说。</strong><br>他们说谜题在学院的每个角落等待的确是对的。但是，你还会发现，当学生不解谜时，他们还可以进行很多有趣的活动！<br><br>这就是介绍的全部！在结束之前，请允许我说一句。。。<br>学院的大门将为所有寻求真正挑战并以迷人故事为核心的玩家打开。我相信那是你，也希望很快能在学院的走廊上见到你。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1155460/extras/796be5c381560720c14dc966f44a0e76.avif?t=1593090475\" width=600 height=121 /></span>",
